If serial number will get the model number, productname, modelproductname for it.\n3. productname is used to set routes in bot whereas modelproductname is passes in ticket and is in accordance with the product name in desk\n4. Returns true if serial number is found in message else false\n5. return the serial number if found in \"SerialNoFromMessage\"\n6. returns product category which will be needed to get faultcodes in case category is not choosen from bot card\n7. This will also get the contact Id in desk as \"DeskContactID\"  using the email linked with the serial number and this contact will be updated in a ticket<\/description><connector>scripts<\/connector><ObjectDefinitions><![CDATA[{\"output\":{\"SerialNoFromMessage\":{\"1\":\"1\"},\"DeskContactID\":{\"1\":\"1\"},\"GotSerialNumber\":{\"1\":\"1\"},\"ModelProductName\":{\"1\":\"1\"},\"modelnumber\":{\"1\":\"1\"},\"productname\":{\"1\":\"1\"},\"category\":{\"1\":\"1\"}},\"inputs\":{\"1\":{\"ConversationID\":{\"1\":\"1\"},\"VisitorChannel\":{\"1\":\"1\"}}}}]]><\/ObjectDefinitions><ExecutorDetail><![CDATA[// Initialize response map\nresponse = Map();\n// Check if session contains \"ConversationID\"\n// VisitorID=\"11240000008702025\";\nif(session.containsKey(\"ConversationID\"))\n{\n\t// Retrieve Visitor ID from session\n\tVisitorID = session.get(\"ConversationID\").get(\"value\");\n}\n// \nif(session.containsKey(\"VisitorChannel\"))\n{\n\t// Retrieve Visitor channel from session to identify whether to get the first message or last message in a list\n\tVisitorChannel = session.get(\"VisitorChannel\").get(\"value\");\n}\n// Get the current time minus 5 minutes (to fetch recent messages)\ncc = zoho.currenttime.subMinutes(5).toString().unixEpoch(\"GMT+5:30\");\n// Fetch recent conversation messages from Zoho SalesIQ API\nconversation_list = invokeurl\n[\n\turl :\"https://salesiq.zoho.in/api/v2/heroelectronix820/conversations/\" + VisitorID + \"/messages?limit=100&from_time=\" + cc\n\ttype :GET\n\tconnection:\"desktosalesiq\"\n];\n// Get the total number of messages retrieved\nno_of_msg = conversation_list.get(\"data\").size();\n// Get the most recent message text\nif(VisitorChannel == \"website\")\n{\n\t// In case of website first entered message is on first in a list\n\trecent_message = conversation_list.get(\"data\").get(0).get(\"message\").get(\"text\");\n}\nelse\n{\n\t// In case of whatsapp first entered message in in last in a list\n\trecent_message = conversation_list.get(\"data\").get(no_of_msg - 1).get(\"message\").get(\"text\");\n}\n// Convert message into a list and get the last word from the message\nrecent_message = recent_message.toList(\" \");\nrecent_message = recent_message.get(recent_message.size() - 1);\nrecent_message = ltrim(recent_message);\n// Create search query to find a matching device in Zoho CRM\nsearch_query = \"(Name:equals:\" + recent_message + \") and (Device_Status:equals:\" + \"Active\" + \")\";\nSearchDevice = zoho.crm.searchRecords(\"Device\",search_query);\n// If no active device is found in CRM\nif(SearchDevice.size() <= 0)\n{\n\tGotSerialNumber = \"No\";\n\tSerialNoFromMessage = \"Null\";\n\t// If the recent message starts with \"IN\" (indicating a possible serial number)\n\tif(recent_message.startsWith(\"IN\"))\n\t{\n\t\t// Check if device exists in CRM regardless of status\n\t\tcheck_active = zoho.crm.searchRecords(\"Device\",\"(Name:equals:\" + recent_message + \")\");\n\t\t// If device exists but is not active\n\t\tif(check_active.size() > 0 && check_active.get(0).get(\"Device_Status\") != \"Active\")\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tSerialNoFromMessage = \"The device related to the serial number is not active \";\n\t\t}\n\t\telse\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tSerialNoFromMessage = \"No device found for the entered serial number\";\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\t// Store response values\n\tresponse.put(\"GotSerialNumber\",GotSerialNumber);\n\tresponse.put(\"SerialNoFromMessage\",SerialNoFromMessage);\n\t// Return response if no active device is found\n\treturn response;\n}\nelse\n{\n\t// Fetch device details from Zoho CRM\n\tdevice = zoho.crm.searchRecords(\"Device\",\"(Name:equals:\" + recent_message + \")\",1,1,\"zohosubscription\");\n\tAccountId = device.get(0).get(\"Account\").get(\"id\");\n\t// Retrieve account details using Account ID\n\taccount = zoho.crm.getRecordById(\"Accounts\",AccountId);\n\temail = account.get(\"Email\");\n\t// Search for contact details in Zoho Desk using email\n\tsearchcontact = invokeurl\n\t[\n\t\turl :\"https://desk.zoho.in/api/v1/contacts/search?email=\" + email + \"&sortBy=createdTime&limit=1\"\n\t\ttype :GET\n\t\tconnection:\"desktosalesiq\"\n\t];\n\t// Extract contact ID from search results\n\tgetContactdata = searchcontact.get(\"data\");\n\t// This contactId will be updated in a ticket amd is passes to \"TicketUpdation\" Plug\n\tcontactId = getContactdata.get(0).get(\"id\");\n\t// \tresponse.put(\"DeskContactID\",contactId.toString());\n\t// Mark Serial Number as found\n\tGotSerialNumber = \"Yes\";\n\tSerialNoFromMessage = recent_message;\n\t// Store extracted data in response\n\t// \tresponse.put(\"modelnumber\",modelnumber);\n\t// \tresponse.put(\"productname\",productname);\n\t// \tresponse.put(\"ModelProductName\",ModelProductName);\n\t// \tresponse.put(\"category\",category);\n\tresponse.put(\"GotSerialNumber\",GotSerialNumber);\n\tresponse.put(\"SerialNoFromMessage\",SerialNoFromMessage);\n}\n// Return final response\nreturn This plug is for open tickets in field service department\n2. This will take chosen ticket number as an input\n3. will get time duration between ticket created time and current time\n4. If duration is less than 48 hrs return duration &amp; \"less than\" message else return \"greater than\" message<\/description><connector>scripts<\/connector><ObjectDefinitions><![CDATA[{\"output\":{\"unit\":{\"1\":\"1\"},\"lessthan\":{\"1\":\"3\"},\"greaterthan\":{\"1\":\"3\"},\"message\":{\"1\":\"1\"}},\"inputs\":{\"1\":{\"ticketNumber\":{\"1\":\"1\"}}}}]]><\/ObjectDefinitions><ExecutorDetail><![CDATA[orgId = \"60002147062\";\nif(session.containsKey(\"ticketNumber\"))\n{\n\tticket_number = session.get(\"ticketNumber\").get(\"value\");\n\tif(ticket_number.contains(\"-\"))\n\t{\n\t\tticket_number = timePart;\n\tdateTimeUTC = toDateTime(combinedDateTime);\n\tdateTimeIST = dateTimeUTC.addMinutes(330);\n\tCurrentTime = zoho.currenttime;\n\tdifference = dateTimeIST.timeBetween(CurrentTime);\n\tgetunit = difference.getOccurenceCount(\":\");\n\tif(getunit == 1)\n\t{\n\t\tunit = \"minutes\";\n\t\tdifference_hours =
